*   [vert.x (‚≠ê16)](https://github.com/PharosProduction/ExVertx) - Elixir event bus bridge to Vert.x services using TCP socket.

### Validations

*   [ex\_nric (‚≠ê2)](https://github.com/falti/ex_nric) - Validation for Singapore National Registration Identity Card numbers (NRIC).

items.title: Awesome Quantified Self
items.content_text:
### Books

*   [The Quantified Self](https://www.amazon.com/Quantified-Self-Deborah-Lupton-ebook/dp/B01M0QCSF7/) (2016) - Deborah Lupton
*   [Self-Tracking](https://www.amazon.com/Self-Tracking-MIT-Press-Essential-Knowledge-ebook/dp/B01HNIVBZ4/) (2016) - Gina Neff & Dawn Nafus
